description: Documenting the removal of the desks at the end of a workday. Showcasing the convinience of a close by storage. Or putting this topic together with the "setting up" topic. They are very simliar in general because we talk about time reduction both times. So seeing the storage at end of the day would not be much different from the setup. The viewer would not get much new information. So I propose to put the two topics together and only film the setup footage.
